show.title: Runaway Bride
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/Gepadu
show.description: When John's fiancée Samantha vanishes on their wedding day, his world collapses—literally—landing him in the hospital where compassionate Dr. Lucy treats more than just his physical wounds. As their relationship blossoms into unexpected love, John finally begins to heal from his heartbreak. But just as he embraces this second chance at happiness, Samantha reappears at his doorstep, bruised and desperate, forcing John to confront unresolved feelings and make an impossible choice.
